<subSubSection pageId="22" pageNumber="730" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="22.[1456,2662,719,1378]" pageId="22" pageNumber="730">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1459,1806,1227,1260]" pageId="22" pageNumber="730">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Niobe Ground Squirrelis protected in Indonesia. No recent information onits distribution, status and ecological requirements is available.
</paragraph>
